{"tid":2403680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除了文革與六四，最被人忽略的大屠殺隱藏在中國的「計劃生育門診」","createTime":"2021-02-11T08:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T08:53:54.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75724dbeef3a06df10f36ba69410b71b95c89372","tid":2403680,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheNewsLens/posts/3675718869164242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheNewsLens%2Fposts%2F3675718869164242&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=d754c1e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TheNewsLens/posts/3675718869164242</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：The News Lens 關鍵評論網<br />\n <br />\n【最被人忽略的屠殺，是隱藏在醫院的「計劃生育門診」】#關鍵專欄<br />\n<br />\n計劃生育開始的時候，很多婦女是被強行墮胎，最殘暴的例子就是山東冠縣開展的「百日無孩」計劃，1991年5月到8月，一百天時間不允許有一個孩子出生，不管是第幾胎、計劃內、計劃外，甚至快要臨產的產婦也要一起抓起來。<br />\n<br />\n人太多就搭棚子，集中給孕婦墮胎，有些引產下來的孩子還是活的，則被活活掐死，政府挖了一個大坑把孩子們的殘骸草草埋了<br />\n。<br />\n#中國 #計畫生育 #人口 #一胎化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hsod5wR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsod5wR.png&h=ea2d4053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77227267bac1a8838518ffbac6c6a8fc622250d5","tid":2403680,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d873e1ec14447ad5d12b22a961c487c1c6df0af6","tid":2403680,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"德政"}]}